     function ClearPlaceHolder(input) {
         if (input.value == input.defaultValue) {
             input.value = "";
         }
     }
     function SetPlaceHolder(input) {
         if (input.value == "") {
             input.value = input.defaultValue;

     function EnterEvent(e) {
         if (e.keyCode == 13) {

     var size;
     var $affectedElements = $("p,div,ul,li,a,span,div.fullWidth");
     //var $affectedElements = $("p,div,ul,li,a,span,div.fullWidth topNav bgBlue");
 
     // Storing the original size in a data attribute so size can be reset
 
     $affectedElements.each(function () {
         var $this = $(this);
         $this.data("orig-size", $this.css("font-size"));
     });
 
     $("#btn-increase").click(function () {        
         $(this).prop('disabled', true);
         $("#btn-decrease").prop('disabled', false);
         $("#btn-orig").prop('disabled', false);
 
         if (size == "Small")
             changeFontSize(2);
         else
             changeFontSize(1);
         size = "Big";
         return false;
     })
 
     $("#btn-decrease").click(function () {
         $(this).prop('disabled', true);
         $("#btn-increase").prop('disabled', false);
         $("#btn-orig").prop('disabled', false);
 
         if (size == "Big")
             changeFontSize(-2);
         else
             changeFontSize(-1);
 
         size = "Small";
         return false;
     })
 
     $("#btn-orig").click(function () {
         return originalsize();       
     })
 
     function originalsize() {
 
         $(this).prop('disabled', true);
         $("#btn-decrease").prop('disabled', false);
         $("#btn-increase").prop('disabled', false);
         $affectedElements.each(function () {
             var $this = $(this);
             $this.css("font-size", $this.data("orig-size"));
         });      
         return false;
     }
 
     function changeFontSize(direction) {
         $affectedElements.each(function () {
             var $this = $(this);
             $this.css("font-size", parseInt($this.css("font-size")) + direction);
         });
     }

     //Method to check Cookies values for Applying contrast 
     function setCookie(cname, cvalue) {
         document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";path=/;";
     }
 
     function getCookie(cname) {
         var name = cname + "=";
         var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
         var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
         for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
             var c = ca[i];
             while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                 c = c.substring(1);
             }
             if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                 return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
             }
         }
         return "";
     }
 
     function checkCookie() {
         var contrast = getCookie("contrast");
         if (contrast != "") {
             ApplyContrast();
         } else {
 
 		if(window.location.pathname.toLowerCase() == "/ar/pages/default.aspx")
 	{		
 		$(".top_hint").find("a img").attr('src', '/SiteAssets/Banner/Nesmaak1-Bttn-ar.png');
 	}  
            
         }
     }
 
     function deleteCookie()
     {
         document.cookie = "contrast=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC;;path=/;";
     }

              <div class="ms-rtestate-field">
               <style>
                .announcement {

 }

               </style>
               <div style="width: 100%; height: auto; background-color: #55bceb; display: inline-block;">
                <br/>
                <ul class="columns no_width">
                 <li class="column_left" style="padding: 10px;">
                  <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #ffffff !important;">
                   <strong style="color: #ffffff !important;">
                    <span class="ms-rteFontSize-4">
                     Visit our new Medical City Hospitals website
                    </span>
                   </strong>
                   <br/>
                   <span class="ms-rteThemeForeColor-2-1" style="color: #ffffff !important;">
                    <br/>
                    We are excited to announce the launch of a website dedicated exclusively to our new Medical City hospitals. The website is part of our commitment to helping patients, and other members of the community, get to know our three new facilities - Qatar Rehabilitation Institute, Women’s Wellness and Research Center, and the Ambulatory Care Center - as well as their staff and services.
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                    Our new Medical City hospitals are significantly expanding our capacity and bringing new services and care options to the people of Qatar. Once fully operational, they will house 500 new hospital beds and 3,000 highly trained clinical and support staff.
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                    Explore our new hospitals for yourself - with photographs and 360-degree virtual tours and the option to register for guided tours – we are excited for you to meet our new hospitals.
                   </span>
                   <span class="ms-rteThemeForeColor-2-1">
                   </span>
